SKECHERS x ONE PUNCH MAN collection 
__________________
Super glad to put together a look for Genos with the latest Skechers x One Punch Man items!
__________________
A special chance to get a pair of Skechers x One Punch Man shoes with steps below (applies to Malaysia only):

1. Flw @skechersmalaysia 
2. Tag 2 friends in the comments, tell me your favorite character featured in this collection (Saitama/Genos/Sonic/Tatsumaki) and how they inspire you as a hero!

The lucky one will be selected & contacted by Skechers Malaysia!
*Terms & conditions apply
*ends 06/04/2021

Get this collection on www.skechers.com.my and selected Skechers stores in Malaysia.
